com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.endpoint.navigation

Class TGRoute

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.TGBaseObject
      • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.endpoint.navigation.TGRoute

  • public class TGRoute
extends TGBaseObject
    An object to represent a TallyGo route. The json contents of this route are often passed around in order to create and re-create this object. The existing trip id may be null
